OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, possibly heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes during the morning. Through the
OL,8,Fafternoon, rain will increasingly
OL,9,Fbecome confined to the Pennines, while
OL,10,Fa few brighter spells develop in the
OL,11,Feast. Breezy at times.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA mostly cloudy start with a
OL,14,Ffew outbreaks of rain, mostly over the
OL,15,FPennines.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FDry and warm on Friday with
OL,18,Fhazy sunshine throughout the day and
OL,19,Flight winds. Mild overnight with a
OL,20,Frisk of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
