OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry and warm or very warm
OL,7,Fthrough this period with variable
OL,8,Fcloud, sunny spells and light winds.
OL,9,FTemperatures likely building day by
OL,10,Fday.
